 laurasiatherian tree reconstruction varied with the number of loci and ordinal representatives used, which are likely the two main contributors to phylogenetic disagreements of Laurasiatheria seen in previous studies. Our study provides significant insight into laurasiatherian evolution, and moreover, an important methodological strategy and reference for resolving phylogenies of adaptive radiation, which have been a long-standing challenge in the field of phylogenetics.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Lv, Xue", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Hu, Jingyang", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Hu, Yiwen", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Li, Yitian", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Xu, Dongming", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Ryder, Oliver A.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Irwin, David M.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Yu, Li", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Adaptive radiations", "Coding dataset", "Intronic dataset", "Laurasiatheria", "Phylogenomic analyses", "UCE dataset", "Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/66ea1335905350db3e6a15117f1b6f0b", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/7934ac8d766f1cb1224d2677959f20b751007c4deec5d0601c6ff863a5f05e5a", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/CYCYW6VB", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/CYCYW6VB", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/5325def90ba9bee6b8eb89f9b14d23d8!/b293799-296481", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mamma